things to do to install this software so far

1) install node
2) install bower--doing this can require setting the proper npm prefix as shown below:  
	$ npm config set prefix /usr/local
	$ npm install -g bower
3) install grunt--this can also require setting the proper npm prefix
4) run npm install
5) sometimes you may need to run bower install as well
6) install mongodb, make sure database is running
7) run grunt by typing "grunt" into the terminal. the program should start

